                                                    Jan 17, 2022
                                                </time>
                                                <p class="relative z-10 mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">After almost a decade working as an individual contributor — with a few short stints in engineering leadership-adjacent roles — I &#x27;ve decided to finally make the jump to engineering management.</p>
